import React from 'react'; import styles from '../users/users.module.css' const Users = (props) => { props.setUsers( (users: [ { id: 1, photoUrl: 'https://i.pinimg.com/564x/4d/77/e2/4d77e2ffb4b616928c6242b94f6cfefd.jpg', followed: true, fullName: 'Luda', status: 'I am fine', location: { country: 'Ukraine', city: 'Kiev' } }, { id: 2, photoUrl: 'https://i.pinimg.com/564x/4d/77/e2/4d77e2ffb4b616928c6242b94f6cfefd.jpg', followed: false, fullName: 'Sasha', status: 'I am fine too', location: { country: 'Ukraine', city: 'Kiev' } }, { id: 3, photoUrl: 'https://i.pinimg.com/564x/4d/77/e2/4d77e2ffb4b616928c6242b94f6cfefd.jpg', followed: true, fullName: 'Vika', status: 'I am fine too', location: { country: 'Ukraine', city: 'Kiev' } } ])) return
{ props.users.map( u =>
{ u.fullName }
{ u.status }
{ u.location.city }
{ u.location.country }
) }
}; export default Users;
